    <img src="@Url.Content("~/Content/images/kf1.jfif")" alt="my pic" style="width:100%;height:100%">

    <div class="container">
        <h2>Careers at Khaira Freight | Drivers</h2>
        <p>
            As a young, fast growing company we know how important it is for us to invest in our future.
        </p>
        <h2>How to apply</h2>
        <p>
            Our team treats you with respect, invests in your further training and safety and provides competitive rates
            and benefit packages. If you are interested please fill out the attached Driver application form
        </p>
        <p>
            <strong>
                Please forward completed applications in confidence to:
                <a href="mailto:accounts@khairafreight.com">recruiting@khairafreight.ca </a>
            </strong>
